Just then Stallex crashed through the bases entrance (I think Mustex 
would still be closeby).  He rolls off his bike to get close to the 
ground with an arrow in his bow.

Mustex:  You can get up kid that shot had nothing to do with us.  
Although we might have to pay for that door (oh come on after all her 
moding I can't even post he knocked down the door if it gives some 
excitement to the situation).
